      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "比如教会我的学生如何正确的写论文提纲",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "但凡能听进去一点，我今天就会幸福度上升一点",
