      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "所以你是个乐观主义者？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我感觉你总是很乐观，每天都乐呵呵的",
