      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "所以说我是悲观主义啊，当事情没有想那么严重的时候，我觉得还挺知足的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "对了，我有个问题想问你",
